{"body": "The problem with this is that the password is now required, where it wasn't before.  No?\r\n\r\nIf you're simply looking to change the validation method, an ugly but effective method is:\r\nlocales/en.yml\r\n``` yaml\r\nen:\r\n  activerecord:\r\n    attributes:\r\n      user:\r\n        password_digest: \"Password\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n#5418 addresses the issues with the documentation, and changes the validation language.\r\n\r\nI can see how validating password_digest is a little strange, but the password validation itself should be left up to the programmer.\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5541176", "created_at": "2012-05-06T21:51:33Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6185#issuecomment-5541176", "updated_at": "2012-05-06T21:54:46Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6185, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/erichmenge", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/d309ddb80e1e28e6f8e3a9685d1f8b29?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F54ffc15ef26ae3d74868acd1923d76e0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/received_events", "gravatar_id": "d309ddb80e1e28e6f8e3a9685d1f8b29", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "erichmenge", "type": "User", "id": 552146, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/erichmenge/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380cd0bd3543c15100d208"}, "id": 5541176, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ra